quran[30]{c,v,t}:
  32,1,"Alif, laam, miim."
  32,2,"Jippineede deftere nden, sikke woo alaa e Mu'um, ko immorde ka JeyЙ—o winndere nden."
  32,3,"Walla Й“e mb'ay kaЕӢko (Muhammadu) o fekindi nde? Si ko woni, ko nde goongaare, immorde ka Joomi maa, fii yo a jerrtin yimЙ“e, Й“e jeertinoowo araano e mum ado maaЙ—a, mbelajo'o, Й“e peeway."
  32,4,"Ko Alla woni takЙ—o kammuuji Й—in e leydi ndin, e kon ko woni hakkunde majji, e nder balЙ—e je'egoo. refti O fotondiri ka dow ""Arski"". Alanaa on gaanin makko, giЙ—o wonaa tefoowo. E on mbaajitotaako?"
  32,5,"Homo fewja fiyaakuuji Й—in ka kammu haa ka leydi, refti Й—i Жҙeenga ka makko, e Гұalaande nde emmbere mum woni, duuЙ“i ujunere e ko limoton."
  32,6,"On [fewjoowo fii Й—um on], ko gannduЙ—o wirniiЙ—i e feeГұuЙ—i, pooluЙ—o, jurmotooЙ—o."
  32,7,"Oon labinЙ—o kala hu'unde nde o tagi. o fuЙ—Й—i tagkde neЙ—Й—aЕӢke e loopal,"
  32,8,"refti o waЙ—i geГұngol makko ngol, e sortondiral, immorde ndihal [maniiyu] lo'oЙ—am;"
  32,9,"refi o fotndindiri mo, o wutti e makko ruuhu makko on. O waЙ—ani on nanЙ—e, e j'iiЙ—e e Й“erЙ—e. [Kono] famЙ—i ko njettonton!"
  32,10,"ЖҒe mbii': ""E nee, si min majjii ka leydi, eyoo min ngontat e tagoore hesre?"" Ko woni kamЙ“e e kawrugol e Joomi maЙ“Й“e, ko Й“e yedduЙ“e [Й—um]."
  32,11,"Maaku: ""warata ta on, ko malaa'ikaajo maayde on wakkilaaЙ—o on. Refti ko to Joomi mon ndutteteЙ—on""."
  32,12,"Sinno a yi'atno, tuma nde bonЙ“e Й“en ugginta ko'e-maЙ“Й“e ka Joomi maЙ“Й“e! [lЖҒe mbi'a]: ""Joomi amen, min nji'ii min nanii, rutton min, min ngolla ko moЖҙЖҙi; minen men njananaama""."
  32,13,"Sinno Min muuyuno, Min ngokkayno kala woЕӢkii peewal makki. Ko woni tun, konngol jojjii immorde e An : ""Ma Mi hebbiniray Jahannama on jinna e yimЙ“e, Й“e denndaangal""."
  32,14,"""MeeЙ—iree (lepte Й—en) sabu mbelsindagol mon kawrugol e ndee Гұalaande mon Й—oo. Menen (kadi) Men yejjitii on. MeeЙ—iree lepte luttal, sabu ko ngollatnoЙ—on kon""."
  32,15,"Nganndee ko gooЕӢЙ—inta Aayeeje Amen Й—en, ko Й“en tawЙ“e si Й“e mbaajoraama Й—e, Й“e cuuyiray sujjugol, Й“e subbuhinora jettugol Joomi maЙ“Й“e, kamЙ“e Й“e townitotaako."
  32,16,"Becce maЙ“Й“e Й—en heЙ—e ngoЙ—Й—itoo e lelorЙ—e Й—en, hiЙ“e noddira Joomi maЙ“Й“e kulol e Й—amaa'mu; e kon ko Min ngarsiki Й“e, hiЙ“e mbintoo."
  32,17,"WoЕӢkii (woo) anndaa ko maranaa Й“e e ko Й“uЙ“Й“inta Й“ernde, Й—um ko njoЙ“di ko Й“e gollatnoo kon !"
  32,18,"E on laatiiЙ—o gooЕӢЙ—inЙ—o wa'ay wa on faasiqe? (aa'aa), Й“e potataa."
  32,19,"Si ko Й“en gooЕӢЙ—inЙ“e Й“e ngolli golle moЖҙЖҙe, hino woodani Й“e Aljannaaji weerde jipporde, sabu koЙ“e ngollaynoo kon."
  32,20,"Si tawii non ko Й“e faasiqiiЙ“e, haray femporde Й“en Й—on nden, ko ka Yiite: Tuma kala Й“e faalaa jaltugol e magge, Й“e ruttitee e magge, Й“e wi'anee: ""MeeЙ—ee lepte Yiite nge pennatoЙ—on ngen""."
  32,21,"Ma Min meeЙ—inir Й“e lepte aduna, ado lepte mawЙ—e Й—en (La'akara),mbelajo'o, Й“e nduttitoto."
  32,22,"Alaa Й“urЙ—o tooГұde wano baajoraaЙ—o Aayeeje Joomi mun Й—en, refti o Й—uurnii Й—e ! Pellet, Meonen, ko Men yoftotooЙ“e e bonЙ“e Й“en."
  32,23,"GooЕӢЙ—ii Min ngokkii Muusaa deftere nden, - wota a wonu e sikke e fii hawroygol e makko -, Min mbaЙ—i nde Й—oworde Й“iЙ—Й“e Israa'iila Й“een."
  32,24,"Min mbaЙ—i e maЙ“Й“e ardiiЙ“e, Й—owirooЙ“e (yimЙ“e Й“en) yamiroore Amen, nde Й“e muГұГұinoo, Й“e woni yananaaЙ“e e aayeeje amen Й—en."
  32,25,"Pellet, Joomi maa, ko KaЕӢko senndoyta hakkunde maЙ“Й“e, Г‘ande Darngal, e kon ko Й“e luutrnoo e fii mum."
  32,26,"E feeГұanaani Й“e, no foti Й—uuЙ—ude e ko Min kalki ado maЙ“Й“e e gire, hiЙ“e yaha e koЙ—ooli maЙ“Й“e? Pellet, no e Й—um, tasakuyeeji ! E Й“ee haqqiltaa?"
  32,27,"E Й“e njiaani, won'de MiЙ—en coggira ndiyam Й—am ka leydi hokkundi, Min njaltinira Й—am remuru, ndu neemoraaЙ—i maЙ“Й“e e kamЙ“e Гұaamata e mum? E Й“e nji'ataa?"
  32,28,"HiЙ“e mbi'a: ""Ko holnde tuma woni ngal uddital, si on laatike gooЕӢЙ—Й“e?"""
  32,29,"Maaku: ""Г‘ande uddial ngal, ko heeferЙ“e Й“en gooЕӢЙ—inoyta nafoytaaЙ“e, wonaa kamЙ“e ngoni neeЙ“nanteeЙ“e !""."
  32,30,"ЖҠuurno Й“e, kaЙ“Й“ito-Й—aa. KamЙ“e , ko Й“e haЙ“Й“itiiЙ“e (lepte)."
